About Me

At nine, I discovered the addictive nature of putting thoughts to paper. By my teens, journals had turned into a WordPress blog, and I was living my Carrie Bradshaw moment. Today, I’m a copywriter with eight years of advertising experience and a deep passion for storytelling. Let’s connect!
